#: ../../source/training/tot/501_adult_learning.rst:173
# 24c11142a11c40deac7e111110131f2d
msgid "Adult like to learn something that practicable, useful, and has benefit for their life. Most adult has a lot of theoretical knowledge. In that case, learning materials for adult should be practicable and can be useful for their life."
