#: ../../source/training/tot/501_adult_learning.rst:182
# 5123260c7f4c41fea5e3eb2318eba343
msgid "Adult is learning by exchange their idea with other people. Because ther are rich of experiences, an exchange idea is the effective way for them to learn."
